data.description: This home is ready for you! Nice sized lot set in a coveted Stockwell Place! Great school ratings! Convenient location for schools, and shopping I-220, I-20, Hwy 80, Harrah's La Downs is minutes away! New roof, vaulted high ceilings and crown molding with fresh paint, new flooring, new stovetop. 2 car garage, nice backyard. Don't miss this one!!
